\mathbb{R}^{3} \smallsetminus A
A=\{(x,y,z): y=0,x^{2}+z^{2}=1\} \cup \{(x,y,z): y=z=0, x \ge 1\}
B=\{(x,y,z): x^{2}+y^{2}+z^{2} > 1\}
